{"tid":1326241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好俾港共呃到，雙普選係唔夠！","createTime":"2019-07-17T06:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T07:50:29.000Z","uid":32204,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96ab1fab964475a71497f9db382caccdce4e820a","tid":1326241,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"近幾年香港出現咁多問題，大家真係認為五大訴求入面頭四大再加雙普選就夠？<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得<span style=\"color: red;\">入閘同宣誓</span>？仲畀港共 keep 住呢個權力，你永遠都唔有真正代表到自己嘅議員，就算你泛民入去過半，佢一樣都可以踢到你唔過半。唔好同我講英國 19 世紀都試過宣誓無效，一黎英國文明過港共好多。二黎香港個投票制度都唔同，就算當初投佢嘅人繼續投佢都未必選得返入去。<span style=\"color: red;\">一定要整走政治審查同宣誓無效</span>。<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得<span style=\"color: red;\">同改法律一樣嘅人大釋法</span>？之前有位巴打請得好好，中國釋法權就好似 programmer，佢寫乜我哋就要點行，無反抗能力。到時外國一無咁關注香港，中共一釋法，咁辛苦爭取嘅普選就會<span style=\"color: red;\">化為烏有</span>。所以一家要<span style=\"color: red;\">畀法庭有釋法權</span>！<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得<span style=\"color: red;\">次次選舉班親中派都玩配票</span>，你其他人點夠中共玩？搞到次次選舉都要大局為重，要有好結果就要含淚，最後<span style=\"color: red;\">引起本土同泛民內鬥</span>。跟本香港個選舉制度有問題，我建議香港可以改做全港唔分區咁行<span style=\"color: red;\">比例代表制</span>，想保留地區代表可以跟德國玩法，等大家真正兄弟爬山，投自己最鍾意嘅黨。<br />\n<br />\n重有就係<span style=\"color: red;\">行政機關主導，權力過大</span>。俾你普選到都唔排除之後嘅政府會硬推啲受爭議議案，同埋特首依加仲要無政黨背景同埋提名。我提議行<span style=\"color: red;\">議會制</span>，等權力分散，政府要不斷向議會負責，無得一意孤行。直接行埋政黨政治。亦都解決選一位特首可能面對嘅制度問題（大黨玩哂、類近政治光譜會𠝹票、多名候選人選最後當選人得票唔過半）<br />\n<br />\n希望可以拋磚引玉，大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a3a3bdc8dde11c5b6d379fcae585a1c2d528fd","tid":1326241,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0065667bab6a4976d33bfb575ebe0f898c28c67d","tid":1326241,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:59:06.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb93eca3c7ba8de9d84d430107244feae442867","tid":1326241,"uid":277888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:59:56.000Z","msg":"我無講嘢"},{"pid":"c1d365dab3d9e6be4def17c2dca1b40597d2528a","tid":1326241,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ec7171effcbf9ebb388dbf92c78c2869026671","tid":1326241,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1d365dab3d9e6be4def17c2dca1b40597d2528a","tid":1326241,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1523798b9711ab6d1a7468a3edd62e17050d1d90","tid":1326241,"uid":119283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5qAWfk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5qAWfk.png&h=a5093f8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4db9ac47a64b6133e11d63bdf220f801ff1e3276","tid":1326241,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:38:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e5833ee76be8f76ca389ac1173426bffb66316d","tid":1326241,"uid":81385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"係三普選<br />\n法官都要選"},{"pid":"df7b84e98a9399e764d83201333c334f7f505228","tid":1326241,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:40:43.000Z","msg":"慢慢嚟啦先針對5大訴求"},{"pid":"cdd446e69b01e7ce9251104543eb6179a5994713","tid":1326241,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df7b84e98a9399e764d83201333c334f7f505228","tid":1326241,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc